data.description: Ready to move in home! Beautiful vinyl wood floors throughout the entire home including bedrooms - NO carpet! Spacious and open living room has lots of natural light and a built-in corner bookcase. Enjoy an open concept kitchen with breakfast bar and lots of storage space. Retreat to the primary bedroom with an en-suite bath with dual sinks and remodeled walk-in shower. Three more bright bedrooms and a full bath with walk-in shower ensure room for everyone! Fully fenced backyard has lots of green space, shed, and NO back neighbors. No HOA restrictions!
